          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> capers</strong> and <strong>black olives</strong> together finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped capers & olives</strong> with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>tapenade</strong></p>",
